https://developer.mozilla.org/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Map
誤った例 let wrongMap = new Map() wrongMap[&#39;bla&#39;] = &#39;blaa&#39; wrongMap[&#39;bla2&#39;] = &#39;blaaa2&#39; console.log(wrongMap) // Map { bla: &#39;blaa&#39;, bla2: &#39;blaaa2&#39; } console.log(wrongMap.get(&#39;bla&#39;)); 正しくは let rightMap = new Map() rightMap.set(&#39;bla&#39;, &#39;blaa&#39;); rightMap.set(&#39;bla2&#39;, &#39;blaaa2&#39;); console.log(rightMap) // Map { bla: &#39;blaa&#39;, bla2: &#39;blaaa2&#39; }
